Hello Everyone!
I'm Jules! I am the emotional support provider for 12 chickens, three guinea fowl, two dogs, one kitten, two Kune Kune pigs, two children, one husband, and a banana spider named Randy.  When I'm not doing all the things for my family and the farm, I write fresh content and explore SEO trends. While I know I should niche, I just can't.  I love writing about new topics and exploring new markets. Somewhere along the way, I started a business, Spilled Coffee Content, and have worked with both fantastic and awful clients since! Thanks for having me, and I am looking forward to meeting new people and forging new relationships in the content world!
